    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy luster, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving. There are no major dents or deep scratches to speak of. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, with all other seating surfaces appearing near-new. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system and heated seats, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound with a full service history available. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. We recently replaced the front brake pads and performed a fresh synthetic oil change. The alloy wheels are in great shape, though the rear passenger rim has a small area of curb rash. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring plenty of miles before replacement is needed. This is a solid, reliable vehicle that balances performance with everyday practicality.",
      "price": 31500.0,
